--1.  In Search Bar, hit Ctrl + Shift + P to allow for commands
--2.  Here are some git commands that should lead to what is needed:
      
        setting the url:  git remote set-url origin {your-new-url
        adding multipe remotes:  git remote add origin {your-new-url}
        remove repository:  git remote remove {name of git repository}
        add repository:  git remote add {url of git repository}

